OL,3,CCrews called to tackle fire at
OL,4,Cderelict Niceday office building in
OL,5,CHampshire
OL,7,FFirefighters have been tackling a fire
OL,8,Fat a derelict office block in Andover,
OL,9,FHampshire.
OL,11,FCrews from Hampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,12,FFire and Rescue were called to
OL,13,FGreenwich Way on Tuesday afternoon,
OL,14,Fwhere fire and smoke could be seen
OL,15,Fcoming from the former Niceday offices.
OL,17,FThe road was closed immediately while
OL,18,Fcrews dealt with the fire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
