OL,5,CHampshire
OL,7,FPeople driving nearby were urged to go
OL,8,Fcarefully as the smoke affected
OL,9,Fvisibility on local roads.JResidents
OL,10,Fliving in the area are advised to
OL,11,Fclose their doors and windows.
OL,13,FHampshire & Isle of Wight Fire and
OL,14,FRescue Service has been contacted for
OL,15,Fan update.
